Tamara Mellon: A Quick Stay in Bankruptcy and Partnership With NEA
The buzzy but bankrupt brand is looking to reemerge with the help of venture capital giant New Enterprise Associates. 


































						By Evan Clark¬†on¬†December 3, 2015					

































































				Share This Article
				











							Reddit						








							LinkedIn						








