Coverage


January 15, 2016
Tamara Mellon Brand Wins Ch. 11 Plan Confirmation
A Delaware bankruptcy judge on Friday confirmed the Chapter 11 plan for Tamara Mellon Brand, the designer clothing line created by the co-founder of the Jimmy Choo designer shoe label, over the strong objections of the company's original investors who pushed for certain loans to be restyled as equity.





